vaulthalla (0.33.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  - Implemented a low-prompt, conservative install policy removing routine debconf prompts from the default path.
  - Added support for Debian changelog updates with distribution and urgency options.
  - Optional local PostgreSQL bootstrap now occurs only if local PostgreSQL is present and healthy.
  - Added Certbot support for nginx setup with domain options.
  - Enhanced setup and teardown command implementations.
  - Refactored AI release process for better draft output handling.
  - Added cached draft support and improved scratch directory management for changelogs.
  - Implemented release contract tests for the Debian install flow.

 -- Cooper Larson <cooper@valkyrianlabs.com>  Tue, 21 Apr 2026 23:11:51 +0000
